    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t « All Events\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tTREASURE FAIR 2026\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tJuly 15, 2026 - July 18, 2026\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tJuly 15-18 | ArtSpring’s biggest fundraiser of the year is back! With furnishings, jewelry, artworks, musical instruments, sporting equipment, collectibles, professional services, and more, Treasure Fair is the perfect place to build your treasure trove and support Salt Spring’s arts community in the process. The last two Treasure Fairs were ArtSpring’s most successful yet, and we’re looking to keep the momentum rolling.\nEvery dollar raised at Treasure Fair goes directly to ArtSpring. Support Treasure Fair by donating, volunteering, or bidding to help ArtSpring in its mission to enrich, uplift, and connect our community through arts and culture.\nREGISTER: to bid and to receive an invitation to the Sneak Peek Gala Event before bidding goes live, register at treasurefair.artspring.ca\nDONATE: To donate items, services, or experiences to our silent auction, head to the “Item Donation” tab at treasurefair.artspring.ca\nVOLUNTEER: If you wish to  volunteer, please email treasure@artspring.ca\nKEY DATES:\nWed June 17: Last day for donations\nWed July 1: Online Catalogue goes live\nWed July 15: Treasure Fair Sneak Peek Gala for registrants and donors: 4pm-6pm\nWed July 15: Online bidding goes live at 6pm\nThur July 16: In-person viewing open to everyone: 10am-4pm, ArtSpring Gallery\nFri July 17: In-person viewing open to everyone: 10am-4pm, ArtSpring Gallery\nFri July 17: Treasure Fair Concert: VAN DJANGO\nSat July 18: In-person open to everyone: 10am-4pm, ArtSpring Gallery\nSat July 18: Bidding closes at 6pm\nBUY CONCERT TICKETS\n \n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tStart:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t July 15, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEnd:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t July 18, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Categories: ArtSpring Presents 2024-2025, ASP-slider\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t treasurefair.artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tAdd to calendar\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tGoogle Calendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tiCalendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook 365\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook Live\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tStart:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t July 15, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEnd:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t July 18, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Categories: ArtSpring Presents 2024-2025, ASP-slider\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t treasurefair.artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\n\t\n    \n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Navigation\n\t\t\n\t\t\t« LOBBY EXHIBITION: Life in Glass\n\t\t\tTREASURE FAIR CONCERT: Van Django »\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t"
