        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;&nbsp; A male stripper parody and improv comedy show The award winning improv comedians are back with a new show, more moves and even quicker wits. A SHOW FOR ALL [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
