    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t « All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tSalt Spring Community Showcase\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tApril 17, 2026 @ 7:30 pm - 10:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$10 – $30\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSalt Spring Community Showcase 2026, Live at ArtSpring – April 17, 2026 | 7:30 PM\nOne night. Endless talent. All Salt Spring.\nGet ready for an unforgettable evening of creativity, passion, and performance as ArtSpring RoundTable proudly presents the Salt Spring Community Showcase — a dynamic celebration of the artistic spirit that makes our island so extraordinary.  On April 17, 2026, the stage comes alive with an incredible array of local talent. Expect the wonderfully unexpected — this one-night-only event brings together performers from all over Salt Spring to share their creativity in front of a live audience.\nThe Salt Spring Community Showcase spotlights the incredible creative voices in our own backyard. It’s a community celebration.\nFeaturing:\n-Wesley Hardisty’s traditional Northern, Métis, West Coast contemporary, and original instrumental fiddle music\n-Matthew McKinney’s musical storytelling\n-GISPA, with a scene from “The Little Prince”\n-Tangle McClaron’s driftwood puppet theatre\n-Lisa Maxx’s lullabies\n-Marilyn Walker & Edgar Hann’s celebration of Newfie and Irish music\n-With Grace Jordan on the mic as MC!\nJoin us for a magical night that puts a spotlight on who we are and what we create, together. If it’s created on Salt Spring, it belongs on this stage.\nBUY TICKETS\n \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t April 17, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 10:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 – $30 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Categories: ArtSpring Presents, ArtSpring Presents 2025-26\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tAdd to calendar\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tGoogle Calendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tiCalendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook 365\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook Live\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t April 17, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 10:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 – $30 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Categories: ArtSpring Presents, ArtSpring Presents 2025-26\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\n\t\n    \n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Navigation\n\t\t\n\t\t\t« MAKANA YOUTH CHOIRS: Spring Term\n\t\t\tCancelled – FIRE & GRACE – Cancelled »\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t"
