        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t « All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tBallet Kelowna Dance Workshop: Advanced Repertoire\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tMarch 22, 2026 @ 4:15 pm - 5:15 pm\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\tEvent Series\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t(See All)\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \nJoin us for a wonderful opportunity to experience a professional ballet class with Ballet Kelowna.\nParticipating in a ballet class led by a professional ballet dancer/teacher is truly a gift to all of us who love ballet dancing. New insights and a deeper understandings of the ballet form nourish our bodies with new sensations of freedom, grace, and skill.\n \nBallet Kelowna and ArtSpring are offering 2 community ballet workshops:\nSunday March 22nd | 3:00pm | Jr/Int/Adv Students: Ballet Barre and Centre\nClick here to register for the all levels class\n \nSunday March 22nd | 4:15pm | Advanced Students: Learning Repertoire (Pointe shoes are optional for the advanced class.)\nClick here to register for the advanced repertoire \n \nPrice: $20/each or $35 for both classes. Space is limited.\nParticipants of the Advanced Learning Repertoire are encouraged to take the All Levels Barre and Centre class to ensure they are warmed up for the Advanced class.\nLocation: Antler Ridge Dance studio 211 Horel Rd W, Salt Spring Island, BC V8K 2A4. 250-537-6537\n \n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t March 22, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4:15 pm - 5:15 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\tSeries: \n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tBallet Kelowna Dance Workshops\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: ArtSpring Presents\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t