        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Fri Oct 24, 7:30pm | Part stand-up, part storytelling, and all heart, this sharp solo show by autistic comedian and author Michael McCreary explores the misconceptions and everyday realities of [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
