        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t « All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\tEvent Series:\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\tNew and Selected Paintings by Margarite Sánchez\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tLobby Exhibition: New and Selected Paintings by Margarite Sánchez\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tNovember 1, 2025 @ 10:00 am - November 30, 2025 @ 2:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\nWhy not celebrate the beauty that surrounds us, the love that connects us, and the preciousness of this wild and beautiful life?\nThis collection of original oil paintings, by Margarite Sánchez, reflects on the extraordinary and ordinary moments that make this ephemeral existence so rich.\nThrough the tender vulnerability of the human body, the lush mystery of the landscape or the quiet intimacy of a still life, each piece is an invitation to slow down, look deeply, and savour the joy of being alive.\nDrawing on timeless themes and guided by curiosity, Sánchez brings a bold contemporary lens to the natural and the sensual.\nStrong angular lines, rich vibrant earth tones and bold brushstrokes evoke the spirit of Abstract Expressionism capturing emotion, beauty, and personality.\nLobby open Tuesday to Friday 10:00am-2:00pm and when the building is open for other activities.\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tStart:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t November 1, 2025 @ 10:00 am \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEnd:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t November 30, 2025 @ 2:00 pm \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\tSeries: \n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tNew and Selected Paintings by Margarite Sánchez\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: Lobby Exhibits\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tMargarite Sánchez\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEmail\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tmasanchez@shaw.ca\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring – Lobby \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tPhone\n\t\t\t\t\t 250.537.2102 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tAdd to calendar\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tGoogle Calendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tiCalendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook 365\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook Live\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tStart:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t November 1, 2025 @ 10:00 am \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEnd:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t November 30, 2025 @ 2:00 pm \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\tSeries: \n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tNew and Selected Paintings by Margarite Sánchez\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: Lobby Exhibits\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tMargarite Sánchez\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEmail\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tmasanchez@shaw.ca\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring – Lobby \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tPhone\n\t\t\t\t\t 250.537.2102 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\