        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Pacifis Sands Resort Tofino Reflections is a collection of photographic works amassed over the past quarter century. These images explore the varying temperatures of the sun\\'s refraction across the globe [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
